# kyoos — User mobile app (Expo SDK 55)

Backend at `../server`. When server changes, verify Axios response shapes used in sagas and **socket.io event names** consumed by this app. Types are hand-maintained mirrors — there is no shared types package.

## Stack

Expo SDK 55 · RN 0.83 · Expo Router · Redux Toolkit + Redux Saga · Redux Persist · Axios · socket.io-client · react-native-maps · Vision Camera · PDF viewer · Calendars.

## Layout

- `app/` — Expo Router routes
- `components/`, `constants/`
- Redux store, slices, sagas in tree

## Workflows

- `npm run start` / `expo start`
- `npm run ios`, `npm run android`
- `npm run build:ios:prod:local`, `npm run build:android:prod:local`

## Skills

- `upgrading-expo` (SDK bumps)
- `building-native-ui`, `native-data-fetching`
- `expo-tailwind-setup`, `expo-dev-client`
- `expo-deployment`, `expo-cicd-workflows`
- `expo-api-routes`, `expo-module`, `use-dom`

Skill versions pinned in `../skills-lock.json`. See `../CLAUDE.md` for cross-app context.
